synopsis: Sardar Udham is a 2021 Indian Hindi-languagebiographical historical drama film based on the life of Udham Singh,a revolutionary freedom fighter highly known for assassinating Michael O'Dwyer in London to avenge the 1919 Jallianwala Bagh massacre in Amritsar.[1]Starring Vicky Kaushal as Singh, the film is directed by Shoojit Sircar andproduced by Rising Sun Films in collaboration with Kino Works.[2] The filmpremiered on 16 October 2021 on Amazon Prime Video.
title: Sardar Udham
